---
title: Sweet Chicken and Pineapple Skewers with Potato Salad
description: Grab the kids and get ready for a fun family meal everyone can help with. Pineapple, pepper and BBQ-spiced chicken skewers get a kiss from the grill! Creamy potato salad is the perfect savoury side to balance out this  BBQ dinner.
